review_blob: Enjoyable and it sticks to the palate like most lithuanians, however this one presents with a creamy flavor that goes outstanding with a trail/party mix and the beer itself almost has a hint of that flavor to it.

Delicious, I spent a few months in brasil in 2004 and drank my fill of these, absolutely delicious.  Ive been looking for a distributor that carries this to the US and have had no such luck.  Brasils best for sure
